Date: Sat, 6 Jul 2013 23:05:19 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] Anti Dupe

Remove CraftBukkit "Feature" of ItemStack's having infinite use if less than 0 stack size.
Blocks most cases of < 0 itemstack dupe bugs
---
